Name: Megha Jangada
Description: Meet Megha Jangada, the visionary founder of our foundation. With a heart deeply rooted in her hometown of Mul and its surrounding areas, Megha is driven by an unwavering commitment to enhance education within her community. Her passion for transforming lives through education has led her to spearhead innovative initiatives aimed at empowering individuals and enriching their futures. Through her relentless dedication and boundless determination, Megha continues to inspire positive change, making a profound impact on the lives of countless individuals in Mul and beyond.
